# thoth_pack_assignment

Assigns a compliance pack to a target agent and tracks assignment status.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_pack_assignment" "cis_agent" {
  agent_id            = var.agent_id
  pack_id             = "cis-l1"
  environment         = "prod"
  approval_policy_id  = "pol-123"
  overrides_json      = jsonencode({
    exempt_paths = ["/tmp", "/var/tmp"]
  })
}
```
